## Benefits

- **Fast creation** - Skips template selection
- **Auto-categorized** - Tagged as feature/enhancement
- **Rich planning** - Claude generates comprehensive descriptions
- **User-focused** - Includes user stories and acceptance criteria
- **Immediate action** - Option to start building right away
- **Team alignment** - Clear feature documentation in Linear

## Feature Complexity Detection

Claude can detect feature complexity and offer to break it down:

**Simple Feature** (1-2 days):
- Single component or page
- No external dependencies
- Clear implementation path

**Medium Feature** (3-5 days):
- Multiple components
- Some complexity
- May suggest sub-tasks

**Large Feature** (1+ weeks):
- Multiple systems affected
- External integrations
- Claude proactively suggests breaking into sub-tasks

